<!DOCTYPE html>
{% set background = '#262a2d' %}
{% set accent = 'rgb(225 158 91)' %}
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Keres – The Art of Vertical Strategy</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="{{ asset('/favicon-96x96.png') }}" sizes="96x96" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="{{ asset('/favicon.svg') }}" />
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="{{ asset('/favicon.ico') }}" />
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="{{ asset('/apple-touch-icon.png') }}" />
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-title" content="Keres" />
    <link rel="manifest" href="{{ asset('/site.webmanifest') }}" />
    <style>
        @font-face {
            font-family: 'Carolingia';
            src: url('/fonts/carolingia.ttf') format('truetype');
            font-weight: normal;
            font-style: normal;
        }
        @font-face {
            font-family: 'RomanSerif';
            src: url('/fonts/RomanSerif.ttf') format('truetype');
            font-weight: normal;
            font-style: normal;
        }

        .bg-dark {
            background-color: {{ background }};
        }
        .border-dark {
            border-color: {{ background }};
        }
        .text-dark {
            color: {{ background }};
        }
        .hover\:text-dark:hover {
            color: {{ background }};
        }

        .bg-accent {
            background-color: {{ accent }};
        }
        .hover\:bg-accent:hover {
            background-color: {{ accent }};
        }
        .border-accent {
            border-color: {{ accent }};
        }
        .text-accent {
            color: {{ accent }};
        }
        .hover\:text-accent:hover {
            color: {{ accent }};
        }

        .bg-blur {
            backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
        }

        body {
            color: #f3f4f6;
            font-family: 'Inter', 'Roboto', sans-serif;
        }

        h1 {
            text-shadow: -2px 2px 10px #0a0a0a;
        }

        .font-carolingia {
            font-family: 'Carolingia', serif;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        }
        .font-roman-serif {
            font-family: 'RomanSerif', serif;
            letter-spacing: 0.03em;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-dark text-gray-100">
<!-- Hero Section -->
<header class="relative h-screen flex items-center justify-center">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
        <img src="{{ asset('/images/landing-dark.webp') }}" alt="Keres Board" class="w-full h-full object-cover"/>
    </div>
    <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
        <h1 class="font-carolingia text-7xl md:text-9xl text-white m-10">KERES</h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-200 mb-8">The art of abstract play in its purest form</p>
        <a href="#"
           class="px-8 py-3 border border-white text-white rounded-full bg-transparent hover:bg-white hover:text-dark transition font-semibold text-lg shadow-lg bg-blur">Play
            for Free</a>
        <p class="mt-8 max-w-2xl text-gray-300 text-lg">
            Keres draws from classic strategy games and enriches them with an elegant stacking mechanic.
            This innovation opens new tactical territory to explore, where every game challenges your intelligence
            rather than your memory. Fresh playing ground, deep decisions, renewed freedom.
        </p>
    </div>
</header>

<!-- Concept Section -->
<section class="py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12">
        <div class="md:w-1/2">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-roman-serif text-white mb-6">Pure tactics, total freedom</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-4">A two-player duel, no randomness, no hidden information.
                Keres gives you a tactical space where stacking your pieces amplifies their movement, while separating
                them multiplies your threats. No fixed meta, no optimal build. Just you, your opponent, and the
                satisfaction of seeing your strategies come to life on the board.</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-gray-400">
                <li>Zero randomness, complete information</li>
                <li>Your style, your strategies</li>
                <li>Games last 30 to 50 minutes</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-1/2 flex justify-center">
            <div class="w-72 h-72 bg-gray-800 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
                <!-- Replace src with actual gameplay GIF when available -->
                <img src="{{ asset('/images/gameplay-preview.webp') }}" alt="Gameplay Preview"
                     class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-xl"/>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Author/Vision Section -->
<section class="bg-[#232629] py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-10">
        <div class="flex justify-center md:w-1/4 mb-6 md:mb-0">
            <div class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full bg-gray-700 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
                <img src="{{ asset('/images/avatar.webp') }}" alt="Author Avatar"
                     class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-full"/>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-3/4">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-roman-serif text-white mb-2">Vincent Chalnot
                - Web Developer & Indie Game Designer</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg mt-3">
                A lover of abstract strategy games (Go, Shogi, chess), I created Keres to
                recapture what fascinates me: simple rules, infinite depth. As a perfectionist developer and maker, I
                designed every aspect of the project — from game engine to web platform, from engraved pieces to
                interface design.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg mt-3">
                <b>My ambition:</b> build a community around Keres, organize tournaments, and deliver a premium experience
                that honors the classics while opening new territory. Keres is designed to be played online first,
                because that's where we actually find time to play.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Pre-order Section -->
<section class="py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-10">
        <div class="md:w-1/2 flex justify-center mb-8 md:mb-0">
            <div class="w-64 h-64 bg-gray-800 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
                <!-- Replace src with actual box image when available -->
                <img src="{{ asset('/images/board-preview-sm.webp') }}" alt="Keres Box" class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-xl"/>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-1/2 text-center md:text-left">
            <h4 class="text-2xl font-roman-serif text-white mb-4">Collector's Edition</h4>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-2">Pre-order the physical edition and own a piece of strategy
                history.</p>
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">45€</div>
            <a href="#"
               class="px-8 py-3 border border-400 border-accent text-400 text-accent rounded-full bg-transparent hover:bg-accent hover:text-dark transition font-semibold text-lg shadow-lg">Pre-order
                Collector's Edition</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Newsletter Section -->
<section class="bg-[#232629] py-12">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-xl">
        <h5 class="text-xl font-roman-serif text-white mb-4 text-center">Stay Updated</h5>
        <form class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 mb-2">
            <label for="newsletter" class="sr-only">Email address</label>
            <input type="email" id="newsletter" placeholder="Your email address"
                   class="flex-1 px-4 py-3 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 text-gray-100 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-yellow-400"
                   required/>
            <button type="submit"
                    class="px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-400 bg-accent text-dark font-semibold hover:bg-accent transition">
                Subscribe
            </button>
        </form>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 text-center">We respect your privacy. Your email will only be used for Keres
            updates. Unsubscribe anytime.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Footer -->
<footer class="bg-dark py-8">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between text-gray-400 text-sm">
        <div class="mb-4 md:mb-0">&copy; Keres 2025</div>
        <div class="flex gap-6">
            <a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition">Legal Notice</a>
            <a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition">Terms of Sales</a>
            <a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition">Contact</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
